, let him say, 'O Allah, I seek guidance from Your knowledge and power from\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25903,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/02\/05\/dua-night-answered\/","url_meta":{"origin":33210,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication for good at night is answered","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 5, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo Muslim retires for the night in a state of remembrance and purification, then wakes up in the night and asks Allah for goodness in the world and the Hereafter, except that he will be given it.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14646,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/08\/worldly-causes-qada-wal-qadr\/","url_meta":{"origin":33210,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Qadr: Worldly causes are pat of Allah\u2019s decree","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ya'mar al-'Uthri reported: I asked, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, the incantations we use, the medicines which heal us, and our fortifications against the enemy; do they repel anything from the decree of Allah?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThey are part of the decree of Allah.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;",